Barcelona's 16-Game Winning Streak Ended by 1-1 Tie With Sporting Gijon

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-02-12T21:03:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-12/barcelona-s-16-game-winning-streak-ended-by-1-1-tie-with-sporting-gijon.html
Barcelona’s record 16-game winning
streak in Spanish soccer’s La Liga ended tonight with a 1-1 tie
at Sporting Gijon.    David Villa ’s goal with 11 minutes remaining earned
Barcelona the draw at El Molinon in Gijon. David Barral scored
in the 16th minute to give Sporting the lead.  Barcelona is now unbeaten in 21 league matches since
suffering its only loss, 2-0 to Hercules on Sept. 11. Barcelona
increased its lead to eight points over second-place Real  Madrid , which is at Espanyol tomorrow.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  